title: UGG Founder Brian Smith to Speak at KU (Kutztown University of Pennsylvania)
text: ( Source : Kutztown University of Pennsylvania ) October 12 , 2015 KUTZTOWN, Pa. - As part of the College of Business ( COB ) Featured Speaker series, Brian Smith , founder of the world famous UGG Australia Brand will speak at Kutztown University
